{"word":"συμφρονέω","slug":"συμφρονέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>συμφρονέω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>ήσω</el>) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:σύμφρων'><el>σύμφρων</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to be of one mind with, to agree</i>, <b><a href='S:Polybius'>Polyb.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to consider well</i>, <el>ἃ δέον ἦν ποιεῖν</el> <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to collect oneself</i>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}